com.yahoo.sketches.tuple

Class DoubleSummaryFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.sketches.tuple.DoubleSummaryFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SummaryFactory<DoubleSummary>

    public class DoubleSummaryFactory
extends Object
implements SummaryFactory<DoubleSummary>
    This is a factory for DoubleSummary. It supports three modes of operation of DoubleSummary: Sum, Min and Max.
